text: Rodrigo Carrasco (born 18 October 1975) is a Chilean equestrian. He competed in two events at the 2012 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Chilean male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Chile Category:Equestrians at the 2012 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2011 Pan American Games Category:Sportspeople from Santiago
